snippet.title: Microshaft Winblows 98 Playthrough
snippet.description:
A 90s interactive "parody" of Microsoft, popular TV and nerds. This is some hot garbage!

Full playthrough without commentary. Seems like nobody else has made a full playthrough of this yet. Weird...

0:00 - Intro & Billagatchi
6:21 - The Roll Ahead
10:44 - Pinbill
15:27 - Winblows Exploder
20:47 - Star Tech The neXT Generation
22:55 - Mr. Gates' Neighborhood
27:26 - Win Bill Gates' Money
32:05 - Campus Cam
37:07 - Campus Cam
39:58 - Xena Code Warrior
41:47 - Touched by Bill
47:21 - Campus Cam
49:25 - Tech.911
55:15 - Bill Watch
57:47 - Lifestyles of the filthy rich & famous
1:01:33 - Campus Cam (Apple & Microsoft get married - not even joking)
1:07:18 - Larry King Online
1:09:55 - What do you want to buy today?
1:14:52 - Campus Cam
1:18:20 - Campus Cam (Coder confession)
1:21:52 - Micro-Friends (including an AWFUL joke about Matthew Perry)
1:26:38 - The End
1:31:40 - Shut Up
1:34:51 - Credits
